Category Description: ( CSC108H1 and CSC148H1) or ( CSC110Y1 and CSC111H1)
( CSC165H1 and CSC236H1) or CSC236H1 or​ CSC240H1

2.0 credits from the following list, including at least 1.0 credit at the 400-level (see below for additional conditions): STA303H1 or​ STA305H1 (whichever one was not taken previously), STA347H1, CSC401H1, STA414H1 or​ CSC412H1, CSC413H1 or​ CSC421H1, any 400-level STA course; JSC470H1 (Data Science III); CSC454H1, CSC490H1, CSC491H1, CSC494H1, CSC495H1, CSC494Y1.
If a student has not completed STA130H1 then an additional 0.5 credit 300+ level STA course that is not used towards any other program requirement must be completed.
